metadata.name: Symphony No. 3 in G Major, “Incarnation”
metadata.description:
Can this be real?  
Can I document this moment  
To prove that it isn't a hallucination?

This vision can’t be possible  
I have witnessed for hours  
An instance that would otherwise be transient  
Time has frozen in creation.

From ominous clouds and moody greys 
A mysterious shape took form  
A crown of light atop the shadowed king,  
To display earth's coronation.

This clashing, chaotic, serene harmony  
Of earth, light, water and air,  
Performed an orchestra of nature.

Incarnation;  
The universe, delivering signs  
That we are exactly where we’re meant to be.

Artist: Alex Mackenzie  
Location: Na Pali Coast, Kauai, Hawaii
